quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  19,12,"Eeyma Yahyaa nanngir deftere nden doole, min n ngokki mo √Īee√Īal ko o suka."
  19,13,"E Yurmeende immorde ka amen ko o laa…ďu…óo o laatike kuloowo [Alla]."
  19,14,"Ko o …óiggan…óo jipnaa…ďe mo …ďen o wonaani ndunndarankeejo gaa∆īii…óo."
  19,15,"Kisal e makko √Īande o jibinaa e √Īande o maayata e √Ďande o immintintee ko o guuru…óo."
  19,16,"JaŇčto ka deftere Mariyama tuma nde o wo…ó…óitinoo immorde e yim…ďe makko …ďen [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyaŇčkoore."
  19,17,"O jogitii ga ma…ď…ďe wirngallo, min Nuli e makko Ruuhu amen o nanndintinanii mo e …ďanndiŇčke fotondir…óo."
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii jurmotee…óo On immorde e maa…óa si tawii a laatike ko a kul…óo [Alla]."
  19,19,"O wi'i: "Pellet, min ko mi Nulaa…óo Joomi maa…óa fii yo mi okke suka laa…ď…óo."
  19,20,"O wi'i: "Ko hono laatoranta kam suka hara …ďanndiŇčke memaani kam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)"."
  19,21,"O wi'i: "ko nii Joomi maa…óa Daaliri: "∆äuum no newii e am e fii yo min mba…ó mo ma'ande fii yim…ďe …ďen e Yurmeende immornde e amen …óum laatike fiyaake √Ďaawaa…óo"."
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure wo…ó…óitiinde."
  19,23,"Ňäata(qatwere) on fi…ói mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: "Ee hara noon mi maayno ko adii …óum mi laatoo hu'unde yejjitaande"."
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wota a suno gooŇč…óii Joomi maa…óa wa…óii ley maa…óa caatngol."
  19,25,"Ye∆īu(dimmbu) fa'ade e maa…óa jullere tamarohi kin nde li…ďa e ma,a…óa …ďenndu…óe te…ďetee…óe."